Package com.pump.data.branch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Branch<K>
    This is a collection of bean data that keeps track of revisions.
    BranchListener<K>
    This listener supports two methods related to saving a branch to its parent branch.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBranch<K>
    This is a helper class implements or redirects a few basic methods of the Branch interface.
    MemoryBranch<K>
    This is an implementation of Branch that stores all its revisions in memory.
